    <item>
      <title>国库会上升，因为美联储的会议记录揭示了关于暂停平衡表径流的讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/treasuries-rise-as-fed-minutes-reveal-discussion-of-qt-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月美联储会议的几分钟后，美国国库会上升，该政策制定者讨论了暂停或减慢资产负债表的径流，直到政府的债务自负戏剧得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/treasuries-rise-as-fed-minutes-reveal-discussion-of-qt-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 20:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔土著领导人信号支持社会主义者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/powerful-indigenous-leader-signals-support-for-ecuador-socialist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔最强大的土著领导人列昂尼达斯·伊扎（Leonidas Iza）表示，他倾向于在四月的径流选举中支持社会主义候选人，这在紧张的比赛中可能证明是决定性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/powerful-indigenous-leader-signals-support-for-ecuador-socialist</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 20:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼发誓要控制政府支出，加拿大公共服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/carney-vows-to-rein-in-government-spending-cap-public-service-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）承诺将限制加拿大公共服务的规模，并在总理任职时进行计划的支出审查，但没有提供有关他总体上减少政府总体场所的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/carney-vows-to-rein-in-government-spending-cap-public-service-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 19:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在特拉华州的战争刺激法案，以保持企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/musk-s-war-on-delaware-spurs-state-bill-to-hang-on-to-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）在法官击落了他的大量特斯拉薪酬方案，将他的公司移出西部后，与特拉华州与特拉华州开战。现在，第一个州是通过立法大修做出回应，以防止其他大亨跟随他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/musk-s-war-on-delaware-spurs-state-bill-to-hang-on-to-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 18:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队计划在主要机构和筹码的主要机构开枪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/commerce-agency-to-order-mass-firing-of-chips-ai-staffers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国立标准技术研究所是商务部下的一个实验室，正准备开火，作为唐纳德·特朗普总统对联邦政府的全面裁员的一部分，大约有500名试用人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/commerce-agency-to-order-mass-firing-of-chips-ai-staffers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 17:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国正式将毒品卡特尔指定为恐怖组织</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/us-officially-designates-drug-cartels-as-terrorist-organizations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在执行令唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）任职的第一天，美国国务院将在拉丁美洲的八个卡特尔和帮派指定为恐怖组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/us-officially-designates-drug-cartels-as-terrorist-organizations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 17:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉延迟投票，因为反对派要求让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/venezuela-postpones-regional-vote-as-opposition-plans-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉的选举机构将国家和议会选举推迟到5月，因为该国的反对派设定了参加投票的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/venezuela-postpones-regional-vote-as-opposition-plans-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 17:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部为了放弃埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）案面对纽约法官审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/doj-order-to-drop-eric-adams-case-faces-ny-judge-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普司法部在周三对纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）的腐败指控驳回腐败指控的争议，周三在法庭上面临审查，这是对政府对美国起诉的更多控制所做努力的早期考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/doj-order-to-drop-eric-adams-case-faces-ny-judge-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 15:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格斯将在五角大楼寻求8％的支出转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/hegseth-set-to-seek-8-spending-shift-at-pentagon-as-doge-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·海格斯（Pete Hegseth）计划在未来五年内将预计的美国军事支出减少8％的计划将避免西南边境执法，空军的最新无人机计划，核武器现代化和为清洁审计做准备。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/hegseth-set-to-seek-8-spending-shift-at-pentagon-as-doge-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 20:20:46 GMT</pubDate>
